today i practiced intercepting and modifying HTTP requests using Burp Suite.
  WHAT I DID
  intercepted a request using Burp Proxy
  Sent the request to Repeater 
  Modified the request parameter
  Observed how the server responded
  EXAMPLE
  original request
  GET/get?name=Emunah
  Modified request
  GET/get?name=HackerQueen
  KEY CONCEPT
  Repeater allows testers to resend and modify HTTP requests multiple times to observe how a server reacts.
  SECURITY INSIGHT
  changing parameters such as IDs can reveal access control issues such as IDOR(Insecure Direct Object Reference).
  TOOLS USED
  Burp Suite
  Firefoc Browser
  WHAT I LEARNED
  Understanding how to intercept and modify requests is a core skill in web penetration testing.
